org.hanns.demonodes.privateParams

Class DefineIO

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ros.node.AbstractNodeMain
      • ctu.nengoros.time.AbstractTimeNode
        • org.hanns.demonodes.privateParams.DefineIO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.ros.node.NodeListener, org.ros.node.NodeMain

    public class DefineIO
extends ctu.nengoros.time.AbstractTimeNode
    Define number inputs and outputs by means of command line parameters. This node does: sum(DataInputs)*sum(ConfigInputs) + a*sin(b*t) Set the parameters from the command line as follows: ./runner org.hanns.demonodes.privateParams.DefineIO _a:=3 _b:=2 _shouldLog:=true _noDataInputs:=2 _noDataOutputs:=10 _noDataConfigs:=1
